				<div id="head-tag">	




	
						<span class="kicker-bar"></span>
			<a href="/csmlists/special/cover-story">				<span class="kicker story_kicker">Cover Story</span>
			</a>			<span class="kicker-bar"></span>
						







</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
Beyond the picket fence: How one city is creating more affordable housing									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>The single-family home has been the American ideal. But to address the affordability crisis, Minneapolis is embracing an aggressive plan that other cities are watching.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
